; Regression test for issue #1695: Easiest way to make register report display note (%N)?
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1695
; The feature request asked for a way to display transaction notes in the register
; report. This is now supported via --prepend-format '%(note) ' or using %N.

2024/01/01 Grocery Store  ; weekly shopping
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Restaurant  ; dining out
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --prepend-format '%(note) '
 weekly shopping 24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
 weekly shopping                                 Assets:Cash                 $-50.00            0
 dining out 24-Jan-02 Restaurant            Expenses:Food                $30.00       $30.00
 dining out                                 Assets:Cash                 $-30.00            0
end test
